{"tid":2517982,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無一套漫畫可以比得上進擊的巨人？","createTime":"2021-05-05T16:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T04:20:30.000Z","uid":370062,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cb04edaf3fb351b0c59aa01c0c5034711de4acc5","tid":2517982,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"簡直好似一本文學鉅著咁，就係差在睇佢點收尾。<br />\n如無意外應該係史上第一，真係好唔想佢完啊！！！！！<br />\n歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"fb09a46ea6674f75f066c0b433b5699974332af4","tid":2517982,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"巨人裡面嘅角色無對錯，只有身份同立場。<br />\n政治色彩濃厚，可以代入我哋嘅社會。<br />\n刻劃人性更加睇到起曬雞皮。<br />\n如果生存需要理由，咁大概係睇進擊的巨人。<br />\n比起一套漫畫，我覺得係經歴緊一個遙遠嘅時代。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>那一天，人類終於回想起了，曾經一度支配他們的恐懼，還有被囚禁於鳥籠中的屈辱。<br />\n</em></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb13420ea65ba1bcae85bdd0d7d7ca8026ac2299","tid":2517982,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"雖然鋼之鍊金術師都係神（03同FA），但我覺得作品之外嘅反思，巨人更加深層。"},{"pid":"20a7951d3a653534096f13b2ef8aa8cd71e8c5bc","tid":2517982,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"鬼滅呢啲真係提都唔使提<br />\n同巨人差太遠"},{"pid":"a60b89858266524f50805f674e7d1a8560666c53","tid":2517982,"uid":365966,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"孤高之人"},{"pid":"dd38fae32ca1f955389780a71d9fabed0baee419","tid":2517982,"uid":177247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"由中學嗰陣睇到而家，個變化真係好大。"},{"pid":"2911c3256b8277355b555e014c4128c1d75c9a85","tid":2517982,"uid":321789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"你都係想我講手機俠啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6495f3a5bd9465b2d3a427f2ee0ebe9b5b97164","tid":2517982,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"bin 